## Quote Collection

**On Leadership:**
> "I never wanted this. I wanted to save people, not lead them. But Firas is gone, and someone has to. So it's me."

**On Her Role:**
> "I'm a doctor. My job is to preserve life. But some people... some people make that impossible. So I do what I have to. And I live with it."

**On Firas:**
> "He saw something broken and decided to fix it. Not with bandages or sutures. With hope. I'm trying to do the same. But hope is a lot harder to administer than morphine."

**On The Reveal:**
> "You think I'm angry because you lied? I'm angry because you didn't trust me with the truth. There's a difference."

**On Being "Powerless":**
> "I don't need powers to be useful. I have hands that can heal. A mind that can plan. A will that won't break. That's enough. It has to be enough."

**On Moving Forward:**
> "Firas believed in second chances. New beginnings. Better tomorrows. I owe it to him to believe it too. Even when I don't."

